126
00:11:40,733 --> 00:11:44,999
Kada ispracas svoju cerku,
zasigurno places.

127
00:11:45,071 --> 00:11:49,201
Kada ja budem odlazila,
hocete li plakati?

128
00:11:49,275 --> 00:11:50,401
